final was a big goal for our team coming here, and for me especially I know it's going to be an emotional day because it falls on my brother's birthday,\\\" said Downie.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big goal\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"our team\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional day\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"my brother's birthday\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"Downie\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Downie's 24-year-old brother Josh died suddenly from an undiagnosed heart condition in May 2021, less than a week before the start of the Olympic trials,from which she was forced to withdraw.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9819279998591641, \"rank\": 0.017073079542373932, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an undiagnosed heart condition\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fall-out from that incident, and its handling by British Gymnastics, threatened to mark the end of Downie's chances of returning to a third Games, having made her debut at Beijing 2008 at the age of 16.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fall-out\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"that incident\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"its handling\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"Downie's chances\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"a third Games\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"her debut\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"Beijing\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after alsoopening up on the physical and mental abuseshe suffered as a young athlete, Downie was persuaded back into the fold by a new approach to her training programme, and expressed pride at having given herself one last opportunity to return to the Games.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the physical and mental abuseshe\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"a young athlete\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"Downie\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the fold\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"a new approach\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"her training programme\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"one last opportunity\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As I was entering the arena I started tearing up, but they were happy tears,\\\" said Downie.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"happy tears\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"Downie\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really wanted to enjoy today.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been the hardest three years of my life, and if somebody asked me to do it again I do not know if I would.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hardest three years\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I know this is going to be my last Olympics, and to have a moment like today and deliver the routines like I thought I could, it was really special.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 2007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Olympics\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"the routines\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew there were a lot of doubters, but there were also people who believed it was still in there, and it was getting me to believe that that was really challenging, after essentially being at the top of the programme for so long and then sliding down to rock bottom.\\\"\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"doubters\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the programme\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"rock bottom\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Downie has given herself a chance of crowning her career with an individual medal after doing enough to squeze into the uneven bars final.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Downie\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2314}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual medal\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the uneven bars\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her score of 14.666 proved enough to cling onto the penultimate qualifying slot.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her score\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"the penultimate qualifying slot\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Downie will also return in the team final after a solid display from team-mates Georgia-Mae Fenton, Alice Kinsella, Ruby Evans and 15-year-old Abi Martin, the latter of whom held her nerves at bay to deliver an impressive performance on the floor.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia-Mae_Fenton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgia-Mae Fenton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia-Mae_Fenton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia-Mae_Fenton\"}, {\"begin\": 2602, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Kinsella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice Kinsella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Kinsella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_Kinsella\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\", \"score\": 0.989226384895342, \"rank\": 0.010331261436357682, \"text\": \"Ruby\", \"types\": [\"Q7946\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\"}, {\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999964743538691, \"rank\": 3.5256585463825096e-06, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfr